// ItemGrid
// Responsive grid of item cards with search filtering and loading/error/empty states.

FUNCTION handleItemClick(item)
  Calls the onItemClick callback with the selected item.

---

FUNCTION handleSearchChange(e)
  Updates the search query state, which filters the displayed items.

---

FUNCTION ItemGrid(props) -> ReactNode                                     EXPORT
  Renders a search input and a grid of ItemCard components.
  Filters items by name using the current search query.
  IF loading, shows a spinner/skeleton.
  IF error, shows an error message.
  IF no items match, shows an empty-state message.
  Calls handleItemClick when a card is selected.
